abstract: In 2019, the industry’s performance was not quite as strong as the overall stock market’s. Some managers point to political uncertainty over health insurance and drug prices.
snippet: In 2019, the industry’s performance was not quite as strong as the overall stock market’s. Some managers point to political uncertainty over health insurance and drug prices.
lead_paragraph: Until science beats death, disease and disability, the health care industry would seem a wonderful investment. Yet in 2019, it fell a bit behind the broader stock market.

abstract: Some executives at small companies have reservations about President Trump, but also concerns about Bernie Sanders and Elizabeth Warren.
snippet: Some executives at small companies have reservations about President Trump, but also concerns about Bernie Sanders and Elizabeth Warren.
lead_paragraph: When it comes to President Trump’s economic policies, there is not much that appeals to Grady Cope, the founder of a machining and assembly company in Englewood, Colo.

abstract: Do you want to visit Hallstatt? Officials say too many tourists — many of them fans of the blockbuster film — are coming to the 16th-century village just to take pictures.
snippet: Do you want to visit Hallstatt? Officials say too many tourists — many of them fans of the blockbuster film — are coming to the 16th-century village just to take pictures.
lead_paragraph: They arrive by the busload and on ferries, many in pursuit of the perfect photograph for Instagram, others seeking the transcendence of a fairy tale land.
headline_main: This Austrian Village Wants ‘Frozen’ Fans to Let It Go
headline_print_headline: Intrusive Film Fans Test Austrian Town’s Patience

abstract: When policymakers frame “choices” as personal preferences, it distracts from major structural constraints.
snippet: When policymakers frame “choices” as personal preferences, it distracts from major structural constraints.
lead_paragraph: If liberals and conservatives can agree on anything about family policies, it’s this: Parents should have choices.

abstract: Corrections that appeared in print on Friday, Jan. 17, 2020.
snippet: Corrections that appeared in print on Friday, Jan. 17, 2020.
lead_paragraph: A picture caption on Wednesday with an article about a clash between the Democratic presidential candidates Senator Bernie Sanders and Senator Elizabeth Warren misidentified the city where Mr. Sanders was photographed campaigning on Saturday. It was Davenport, Iowa, not Newton, Iowa.

abstract: The dispute has led to negative attacks and doubts about party unity, exactly what Democratic leaders do not want to happen, for fear of handing an advantage to President Trump.
snippet: The dispute has led to negative attacks and doubts about party unity, exactly what Democratic leaders do not want to happen, for fear of handing an advantage to President Trump.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — For a year they offered almost nothing but praise for each other in public, he paying tribute to her populism, she initially adopting his health care plan, and each supporting the other against moderates in the Democratic presidential debates and rebuking reporters who sought to stoke any suppressed rivalry.
